    {
      "para_id": "Q001792.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Enlil , the king of all lands , his beloved master , Amar-Suena , nominated by Enlil in Nibru , the steadfast supporter of Enlil's temple , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters , built the temple in which syrup , ghee , and wine never cease in ( Enlil's ) place of offering ."
    }
  ],
